I can still deal with it myself.

79
00:06:18,795 --> 00:06:19,795
It's fine.

80
00:06:23,755 --> 00:06:25,315
I'm always by your side.

81
00:06:30,795 --> 00:06:31,795
Thank you.

82
00:06:35,755 --> 00:06:39,835
