92
00:07:04,675 --> 00:07:05,355
Well...

93
00:07:06,475 --> 00:07:07,715
I do.

94
00:07:08,315 --> 00:07:09,315
Give it a shot.

95
00:07:09,715 --> 00:07:11,795
Sure. I'll be your assistant, okay?

96
00:07:12,515 --> 00:07:13,675
