107
00:07:46,355 --> 00:07:51,785
♫I should run,
but I'm tied to the sound of you♫

108
00:07:52,795 --> 00:07:57,915
♫Words dissolve in the air,
I'm losing hold♫

109
00:08:01,595 --> 00:08:07,275
♫Pull me close,
now I'm stranded in your waves,♫

110
00:08:07,995 --> 00:08:12,075
