111
00:08:12,115 --> 00:08:12,995
Oh, Babe.

112
00:08:13,715 --> 00:08:15,035
Let me dry your hair for you.

113
00:08:17,115 --> 00:08:17,775
Here.

114
00:08:24,195 --> 00:08:25,435
You're so sweet, Babe.

115
00:08:26,155 --> 00:08:26,995
