122
00:09:08,835 --> 00:09:10,035
Your hair smells so good.

123
00:09:12,659 --> 00:09:14,331
Alright. It's done.

124
00:09:14,955 --> 00:09:15,715
Here.

125
00:09:16,275 --> 00:09:17,395
I've got something for you.

126
00:09:18,570 --> 00:09:19,370
