132
00:09:36,035 --> 00:09:36,915
Really?

133
00:09:43,195 --> 00:09:44,445
Here, let me apply it for you.

134
00:09:52,715 --> 00:09:54,075
Don't mess around!

135
00:09:58,035 --> 00:09:59,355
Stay still.

136
00:10:04,115 --> 00:10:04,955
