Is he feeling better?

167
00:11:47,195 --> 00:11:48,875
The doctor says
he's ready for the surgery.

168
00:11:49,275 --> 00:11:51,555
The only thing that's holding us back

169
00:11:52,035 --> 00:11:54,795
