172
00:12:01,755 --> 00:12:02,715
- Don't worry.
- Mm.

173
00:12:02,755 --> 00:12:04,315
And how's your situation going?

174
00:12:06,275 --> 00:12:07,035
Well...

175
00:12:07,715 --> 00:12:08,715
