225
00:16:45,875 --> 00:16:47,515
Do you want me to keep going?

226
00:17:14,395 --> 00:17:15,995
Do you still want...

227
00:17:16,615 --> 00:17:17,495
I do.

228
00:18:04,675 --> 00:18:05,675
I'll be right back, okay?

229
00:18:29,349 --> 00:18:30,979
